data.description: This stunning home is sure to impress! Situated on a spacious corner lot, this property boasts plenty of outdoor and indoor space for entertaining guests or enjoying a quiet evening under the stars. Inside, you'll find a beautifully designed and well-maintained home that offers ample space for a growing family or those who love to entertain. With its open floor plan, this home features a separate living, dining, family, and breakfast area as well as an upstairs loft. This home is perfect for those who appreciate both style and functionality! Don't miss out on the opportunity to make this your dream home. Schedule a showing today and see all that this amazing property has to offer!
